               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner. Q.</hi> Do you swear that is the shirt? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> It is, I gave it to the policeman a few hours after, when he applied for it—I paid you for it—I have some dozens of shirts in the shop—I gave 9<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. or 10<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. for this—I did not put it among other shirts under the counter—it laid on the counter when the po<lb></lb>liceman came in—I had never put it by—I never bought anything else of you.</p>
